{"tid":1692342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲勸唔掂架啦 由佢啦","createTime":"2019-11-04T04:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:57:25.000Z","uid":24721,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d564ce75f7891c2ad80c760e3a9303255841cb81","tid":1692342,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔可以有咁既想法<br />\n<br />\n尤其係選舉前，尤其係自己既家人<br />\n可能會發生好多事<br />\n但選舉都係一個機會<br />\n<br />\n行事在人 成事在天<br />\n<br />\n如果同父母唔係坦承相對既關係<br />\n請引用其他可靠長輩既說話 例如:「明仔老豆個次好彩有呀邊個幫咋，果個咩都無so佢呀，搞唔掂平時食幾多蛇宴都補唔番啦！投佢把鬼咩！」<br />\n<br />\n拉票多數唔成功，但勸佢唔投某候選人多數唔難，有界票效果<br />\n<br />\n如果都做唔到，佢好堅決：「我平時受佢咁多恩惠，一定要投！」 咁就唯有同佢講，例如：「你投唔投佢鬼知咩，秋高氣爽我地去下郊遊好過啦」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">最後就係當日唔該各位自己早D去投左自己個份先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外話說今朝聽到細妹同老豆講：「住太古個呀邊個同我講佢爭D俾人斬呀，今朝開電視1台竟然話爭執打鬥，佢今朝嬲到打左去廣播局，仲特登打黎叫我呢世唔好睇」<br />\n之後就轉左台了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74d8fcc59d683d535869824969dfa68bbe6de95","tid":1692342,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔使同佢嘈，引佢出去行多啲街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fdb2960b2662fd89c464c8ba97241d7f0132b1","tid":1692342,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b74d8fcc59d683d535869824969dfa68bbe6de95","tid":1692342,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔使同佢嘈，引佢出去行多啲街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"行動代號：孝子賢孫"},{"pid":"cc8c28f58e231e2ae213223d248be59332288bf3","tid":1692342,"uid":24721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b74d8fcc59d683d535869824969dfa68bbe6de95","tid":1692342,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔使同佢嘈，引佢出去行多啲街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:52:20.000Z","msg":"我姨媽佢幫建制做開義工<br />\n<br />\n個日我表哥話車佢地上山頂<br />\n<br />\n仲book左淺水灣酒店同佢地玩埋個半日<br />\n<br />\n中間同佢老婆輪流咁揸番車出去將軍澳投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acefd9ebb90240fbf9d37a45bd381e5782e267d","tid":1692342,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"輸出革命 第一步就係父母<br />\n<br />\n我親身例子係 本身我雙親係藍<br />\n<br />\n依家我媽已經黃到決定唔搭港鐵<br />\n<br />\n爸就深藍變淺藍"},{"pid":"09693e78925b49aee2272de3888f3206ff757691","tid":1692342,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0acefd9ebb90240fbf9d37a45bd381e5782e267d","tid":1692342,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"輸出革命 第一步就係父母<br />\n<br />\n我親身例子係 本身我雙親係藍<br />\n<br />\n依家我媽已經黃到決定唔搭港鐵<br />\n<br />\n爸就深藍變淺藍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f0afa5f1105bbff39275391f0a67cbf53ffff3","tid":1692342,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4dd70a3602a44a653271795ed084196a89b2f1","tid":1692342,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}